HEADWORD: amphoteric
<hw>am`pho*ter"ic</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧m`f⟦osl⟧*t⟦ecr⟧r"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'amfo`teros</grk> both.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Partly one and partly the other</def>⟦br⟧
