<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Especially:</specif> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Having both acidic and basic groups within the same molecule, and
consequently neither acid nor alkaline; neutral.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Smart.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

